(In reply to Markus Keller from comment #7)
> Organize Imports currently adds an unused import for the invalid reference
> "T.super.f" because "f" resolves to a field (even with the patch). "f" and
> the SuperFieldAccess node should not resolve to anything.

Test Case to show the above problem (On Top of Patch (Comment 9)):

